title: Quarterly average daily rate of hotels in Barcelona 2010 to 2017
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 4 different Quarters on X-axis for 8 groups 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, and 2017. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Over the 4 Quarters, the SOME LABEL for both 2011 and 2010 have declined.
Out of all 8 groups, 2015 had the highest SOME LABEL in Quarter Q3 and 2017 had the lowest SOME LABEL in Quarter Q4.
In Quarter Q3, 2011 had the highest SOME LABEL among all 4 Quarters and it has the lowest SOME LABEL in Quarter Q1.
min_summary: This grouped bar chart represents 4 different Quarters on X-axis for 8 groups 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, and 2017. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
All through the Quarters, similar trend was observed for 2011 and 2010. In both cases, the SOME LABEL have declined.

max_summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 4 different Quarters for 8 groups 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, and 2017 that are presented on the X-axis.
Over the 4 Quarters, the SOME LABEL for both 2011 and 2010 have declined.
Quarter Q3 had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 8 groups, and it was for 2015. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Quarter Q4 for 2017.
Among all the Quarters, 2011 had the highest SOME LABEL in Quarter Q3 and lowest SOME LABEL in Quarter Q1.
The maximum SOME LABEL for 2011 that was found in Quarter Q3 was 1.33 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL observed in Quarter Q1.
Out of all 8 groups, the highest gap between the maximum and minimum SOME LABEL was found in case of 2011.
2015 had the maximum SOME LABEL out of all 8 groups in Quarter Q3 followed by 2015 in Q3, and the minimum SOME LABEL is found for 2017 in Q4.
On average, the Quarter Q1 had the highest SOME LABEL for all 8 groups 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, and 2017. Whereas Q4 had the lowest average SOME LABEL.
